WITH stage3_rows AS (
  SELECT *
  FROM (VALUES
    ('cat_feelings_faces_books', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for first feelings exploration', 'When I Feel Surprised', 'Child''s Play', 'Waterstones', 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/when-i-feel-surprised/paula-bowles/childs-play/9781786287496', NULL, '£5.99', 'in_stock', '2 to 3 years', 'A board book exploring the feeling of surprise with colorful creatures and positive statements.', 'This book is an excellent introduction to emotions for nearly two-and-a-half-year-olds. Part of a series developed with a child psychologist, it helps toddlers identify and label a specific feeling—surprise—through relatable scenarios and simple language. The board book format is durable for little hands. It''s perfect for starting conversations about emotions, aligning with the focus on face-naming and simple emotion labelling at this stage.', 'Directly addresses emotion identification and is part of a series covering core feelings, ideal for 28-30m. The simple, non-gendered approach supports early emotional literacy.', 'While highly relevant, the number of online reviews is low, suggesting it might be a newer or less widely reviewed title. However, the expert backing from a child psychologist provides strong validation.', 'buy', true, 'A thoughtful gift for a child with big feelings or a new sibling.', 'Pick gentle stories rather than moral lessons.', '(none)', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.amazon.co.uk/When-Feel-Surprised-First-Feelings/dp/1786287498', 'https://www.goodreads.com/en/book/show/127563582-when-i-feel-surprised', 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/when-i-feel-surprised/paula-bowles/childs-play/9781786287496']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_feelings_faces_books', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for interactive mood exploration', 'Happy as a Lamb: Choose Your Mood, Express Your Feelings', 'Mama Makes Books', 'Waterstones', 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/happy-as-a-lamb-choose-your-mood-express-your-feelings/teresa-bellon/mama-makes-books/9781916780002', NULL, '£7.99', 'in_stock', '2 to 5 years', 'An interactive board book with puzzle pieces to help children identify and express various emotions.', 'This interactive board book is fantastic for 28-30 month olds, offering a playful way to explore a wide range of emotions from happy to grumpy. The chunky puzzle pieces engage fine motor skills while encouraging children to describe their feelings and discover simple mood-lifting activities. It''s a clever tool for opening conversations about emotions and aligns perfectly with fostering early emotional vocabulary and face-naming at this stage.', 'Interactive format and broad emotional vocabulary are excellent for this age. The focus on identifying and expressing feelings through play is highly relevant to the cluster objective.', 'The listed age range extends to 5 years, but the interactive board book format and simple concepts are well-suited for the younger end of this spectrum. Limited public reviews, but strong editorial praise.', 'buy', true, 'A thoughtful gift for a child with big feelings or a new sibling.', 'Pick gentle stories rather than moral lessons.', '(none)', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.booktrust.org.uk/book-recommendations/bookfinder/happy-as-a-lamb-choose-your-mood-express-your-feelings/', 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/happy-as-a-lamb-choose-your-mood-express-your-feelings/teresa-bellon/mama-makes-books/9781916780002']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_feelings_faces_books', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for early calming techniques', 'Just Breathe, Bear', 'Curious Fox', 'BookTrust (listed)', 'https://www.booktrust.org.uk/book-recommendations/bookfinder/just-breathe-bear/', NULL, 'Price not found on BookTrust', 'in_stock', '2 to 3 years', 'A picture book teaching toddlers a simple mindful breathing technique to manage big feelings.', '''Just Breathe, Bear'' is a gentle and effective book for nearly two-and-a-half-year-olds who are beginning to experience and understand big emotions like worry, sadness, and anger. It introduces a simple breathing technique, providing a practical tool for self-regulation. The minimal illustrations make the emotions clear and easy for young children to recognize, supporting the stage''s focus on simple emotion labelling.', 'Offers a practical coping strategy for managing emotions, which is an important aspect of emotional development at this age. Clear, simple illustrations aid emotion recognition.', 'Price and retail availability need further checking as BookTrust is an editorial site. However, the content is highly relevant.', 'buy', true, 'A thoughtful gift for a child with big feelings or a new sibling.', 'Pick gentle stories rather than moral lessons.', '(none)', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.booktrust.org.uk/book-recommendations/bookfinder/just-breathe-bear/']::text[], 'check_price'),
    ('cat_feelings_faces_books', 4, 4, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for celebrating happiness', 'I am Happy', 'Walker Books', 'BookTrust (listed)', 'https://www.booktrust.org.uk/book-recommendations/bookfinder/i-am-happy/', NULL, 'Price not found on BookTrust', 'in_stock', '2 to 3 years', 'A rhyming picture book celebrating happiness and encouraging children to explore what makes them joyful.', 'Michael Rosen''s ''I am Happy'' is a delightful read-aloud for 28-30 month olds, focusing on the positive emotion of happiness. Its simple rhyming text and bold illustrations make it accessible and engaging, encouraging children to identify and express their own joyful feelings. This book perfectly supports the stage''s emphasis on simple emotion labelling and provides a wonderful opportunity for parents to discuss positive emotions with their toddlers.', 'Focuses on a positive core emotion with simple, engaging text and illustrations, suitable for early emotion identification.', 'Price and retail availability need further checking as BookTrust is an editorial site. However, the content is highly relevant.', 'buy', true, 'A thoughtful gift for a child with big feelings or a new sibling.', 'Pick gentle stories rather than moral lessons.', '(none)', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.booktrust.org.uk/book-recommendations/bookfinder/i-am-happy/']::text[], 'check_price'),
    ('cat_feelings_faces_books', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for understanding big feelings', 'Big Feelings (Why? Questions And Answers For Toddlers)', 'Yoyo Books', 'Waterstones', 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/big-feelings-why-questions-and-answers-for-toddlers/9789465055190', NULL, '£8.99', 'in_stock', 'Toddlers', 'A board book using a Q&A format to help toddlers understand and process various big feelings.', 'This board book is a solid choice for 28-30 month olds, using a simple Q&A format to address ''big feelings''. It''s designed to help toddlers understand and process their emotions, which is crucial for this developmental stage. The interactive nature of questions and answers can encourage engagement and discussion, supporting the goal of simple emotion labelling and face-naming.', 'Addresses ''big feelings'' directly with a Q&A format, promoting understanding and discussion, suitable for the age band.', 'General ''Toddlers'' age marking, but content aligns with 28-30m. No specific review data found, but the concept is strong.', 'buy', true, 'A thoughtful gift for a child with big feelings or a new sibling.', 'Pick gentle stories rather than moral lessons.', '(none)', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.waterstones.com/book/big-feelings-why-questions-and-answers-for-toddlers/9789465055190']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_feelings_faces_books', 6, 6, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for budgets', 'What to Do When You Feel Like Biting', 'Cara Goodwin', NULL, 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/what-to-do-when-you-feel-like-biting/cara-goodwin/katie-turner/9798886081534', NULL, '£7.99', NULL, NULL, 'Cara Goodwin — What to Do When You Feel Like Biting', 'Addresses a common toddler behavior linked to strong feelings, offering guidance.', 'Addresses a common toddler behavior linked to strong feelings, offering guidance.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_feelings_faces_books', 7, 7, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for small spaces', 'What to Do When You Feel Like Hitting', 'Cara Goodwin', NULL, 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/what-to-do-when-you-feel-like-hitting/cara-goodwin/katie-turner/9798886081657', NULL, '£7.99', NULL, NULL, 'Cara Goodwin — What to Do When You Feel Like Hitting', 'Similar to the biting book, provides guidance for another challenging behavior driven by emotions.', 'Similar to the biting book, provides guidance for another challenging behavior driven by emotions.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_feelings_faces_books', 8, 8, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for borrowing first', 'Moodypuffs: A Feelings Book For Toddlers', 'Karmen Tartt', NULL, 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/moodypuffs/karmen-tartt/9798349503924', NULL, '£11.99', NULL, NULL, 'Karmen Tartt — Moodypuffs: A Feelings Book For Toddlers', 'General feelings book for toddlers, good for expanding emotional vocabulary.', 'General feelings book for toddlers, good for expanding emotional vocabulary.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_feelings_faces_books', 9, 9, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for gifting', 'Just Now I Feel Angry', 'Adrian Laurent', NULL, 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/just-now-i-feel-angry/adrian-laurent/9798886081657', NULL, '£13.99', NULL, NULL, 'Adrian Laurent — Just Now I Feel Angry', 'Focuses on anger and frustration, offering strategies for managing these specific emotions.', 'Focuses on anger and frustration, offering strategies for managing these specific emotions.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_feelings_faces_books', 10, 10, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for growing with them', 'What to Do When It''s Time to Calm Down', 'Cara Goodwin', NULL, 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/what-to-do-when-its-time-to-calm-down/cara-goodwin/katie-turner/9798886081541', NULL, '£7.99', NULL, NULL, 'Cara Goodwin — What to Do When It''s Time to Calm Down', 'Provides practical calming strategies, complementing emotion identification.', 'Provides practical calming strategies, complementing emotion identification.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_picture_story_books', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for imaginative play', 'Press Here', 'Chronicle Books', 'Waterstones', 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/press-here/herve-tullet/9781452178592', NULL, '£7.99', 'in_stock', '0-3 years (implied)', 'A unique interactive board book where dots respond to touch, encouraging imagination and cause-and-effect learning.', 'This book is a brilliant way to encourage your nearly two-and-a-half-year-old to engage with a story by making things happen. It fosters early understanding of cause and effect, and naturally prompts questions like ''What will happen next?'' or ''What colour is that dot now?''. Skip if your child prefers more traditional narratives.', 'Perfectly aligns with the 28-30m stage by encouraging question-led naming and understanding of simple actions and reactions, a precursor to short story arcs.', NULL, 'buy', true, 'A strong gift if the family enjoys books. Look for sturdy pages and familiar scenes.', 'If you already have lots of board books, choose ones with clearer stories or more to talk about.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.waterstones.com/book/press-here/herve-tullet/9781452178592', 'https://www.mumsnet.com/swearsby/best-books-for-two-year-olds']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_picture_story_books', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for exploring farm animals', 'On the Farm: A push pull slide board book', 'Campbell Books', 'Amazon UK', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Axel-Scheffler-Farm/dp/1509866949', NULL, '£4.50', 'in_stock', '1-4 years', 'An interactive board book with push, pull, and slide mechanisms to discover farm animals and their sounds.', 'Ideal for toddlers who are starting to name objects and make animal sounds. The interactive elements naturally lead to questions like ''What animal is hiding?'' or ''What sound does the cow make?'', building vocabulary and early conversational skills. Borrow if you already have many farm-themed books.', 'Encourages question-led naming and action words, directly supporting the 28-30m stage of linking words together without turning talk into a test.', NULL, 'buy', true, 'A strong gift if the family enjoys books. Look for sturdy pages and familiar scenes.', 'If you already have lots of board books, choose ones with clearer stories or more to talk about.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.amazon.co.uk/Axel-Scheffler-Farm/dp/1509866949']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_picture_story_books', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for everyday object naming', 'Very First Book of Things to Spot At Home', 'Usborne', 'Amazon UK', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Very-First-Things-Spot-Home/dp/147492209X', NULL, '£8.00', 'in_stock', '18 months +', 'A vibrant spotter book encouraging children to find and name everyday objects around the home.', 'This book is excellent for developing your toddler''s vocabulary and observation skills. It naturally prompts questions like ''Where''s the teddy?'' or ''What''s that?'', encouraging them to link words and build simple sentences. Hold off if your child is already proficient in naming household items.', 'Directly supports question-led naming and early explanations by focusing on familiar objects, making it easy for toddlers to engage and form simple questions.', NULL, 'buy', true, 'A strong gift if the family enjoys books. Look for sturdy pages and familiar scenes.', 'If you already have lots of board books, choose ones with clearer stories or more to talk about.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.amazon.co.uk/Very-First-Things-Spot-Home/dp/147492209X', 'https://www.mumsnet.com/swearsby/best-books-for-two-year-olds']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_picture_story_books', 4, 4, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for rhyming and humour', 'Oi Frog', 'Hachette Children''s Group', 'Amazon UK', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Oi-Frog-Friends/dp/1444910868', NULL, '£7.00', 'in_stock', '2-5 years', 'A hilarious rhyming story about a frog who discovers where different animals are supposed to sit.', 'This book is fantastic for introducing rhyme and humour, which can spark lots of giggles and questions like ''What rhymes with cat?'' or ''Where does the dog sit?''. It encourages prediction and playful language, helping your toddler to link words in a fun, engaging way. Borrow if your child is not yet engaging with rhyming patterns.', 'The repetitive and rhyming nature encourages toddlers to anticipate and ask questions, reinforcing early language patterns and linking words together in a playful context.', NULL, 'buy', true, 'A strong gift if the family enjoys books. Look for sturdy pages and familiar scenes.', 'If you already have lots of board books, choose ones with clearer stories or more to talk about.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.amazon.co.uk/Oi-Frog-Friends/dp/1444910868', 'https://www.mumsnet.com/swearsby/best-books-for-two-year-olds']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_picture_story_books', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for interactive giggles', 'The Tickle Book', 'Macmillan Children''s Books', 'Amazon UK', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Tickle-Book-Ian-Whybrow/dp/0230747092', NULL, '£7.00', 'in_stock', '1-4 years', 'A lift-the-flap book featuring various animals and ticklish surprises, encouraging interaction and laughter.', 'This book is perfect for interactive play, with lift-the-flaps and tickling actions that naturally lead to questions like ''Who''s under here?'' or ''Where should we tickle next?''. It''s a great way to build connection and encourage participation, helping your toddler to engage with simple stories and actions. Bring back out if your child enjoyed it at an earlier stage, as the interactive elements will still be engaging.', 'The interactive elements and simple narrative encourage toddlers to ask questions about actions and characters, fostering early story comprehension and conversational skills, aligning with the 28-30m stage of telling little stories.', NULL, 'buy', true, 'A strong gift if the family enjoys books. Look for sturdy pages and familiar scenes.', 'If you already have lots of board books, choose ones with clearer stories or more to talk about.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.amazon.co.uk/Tickle-Book-Ian-Whybrow/dp/0230747092', 'https://www.mumsnet.com/swearsby/best-books-for-two-year-olds']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_picture_story_books', 6, 6, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for budgets', 'National Trust: My Very First Spotter''s Guide: I Spot a Rabbit', 'Nosy Crow Ltd', NULL, 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/National-Trust-Spotters-Rabbit-Guides/dp/1805132733', NULL, '£7.99', NULL, NULL, 'Nosy Crow Ltd — National Trust: My Very First Spotter''s Guide: I Spot a Rabbit', 'Spotter guide encourages observation and naming, fostering questions and vocabulary development. Age-appropriate (2-3 years).', 'Spotter guide encourages observation and naming, fostering questions and vocabulary development. Age-appropriate (2-3 years).', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_picture_story_books', 7, 7, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for small spaces', 'Let’s go home, Baby Chick', 'Nosy Crow', NULL, 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Lets-Go-Home-Baby-Chick/dp/1839949937', NULL, '£7.49', NULL, NULL, 'Nosy Crow — Let’s go home, Baby Chick', 'Interactive board book with moving sliders, encourages children to help animals find their way home, fostering questions and problem-solving. Age-appropriate (2-4 years).', 'Interactive board book with moving sliders, encourages children to help animals find their way home, fostering questions and problem-solving. Age-appropriate (2-4 years).', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_picture_story_books', 8, 8, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for borrowing first', 'Story Path: An Interactive Board Book for Toddlers Where You Choose Your Own Adventure', 'Little Tiger Press', NULL, 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Story-Path-Kate-Baker/dp/1835872867', NULL, '£9.99', NULL, NULL, 'Little Tiger Press — Story Path: An Interactive Board Book for Toddlers Where You Choose Your Own Adventure', 'Choose-your-own-adventure format encourages decision-making and imagination, leading to questions about choices and outcomes. Highly interactive.', 'Choose-your-own-adventure format encourages decision-making and imagination, leading to questions about choices and outcomes. Highly interactive.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_picture_story_books', 9, 9, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for gifting', 'We''re Going on a Bear Hunt: My First Opposites', 'Walker Books Ltd', NULL, 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Were-Going-Bear-Hunt-Opposites/dp/1406399531', NULL, '£6.99', NULL, NULL, 'Walker Books Ltd — We''re Going on a Bear Hunt: My First Opposites', 'Interactive adventure based on a classic, teaches opposites and encourages finger-tracing. Good for early concepts and conversation.', 'Interactive adventure based on a classic, teaches opposites and encourages finger-tracing. Good for early concepts and conversation.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_picture_story_books', 10, 10, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for growing with them', 'We''re Going on a Bear Hunt: My First 123', 'Walker Books Ltd', NULL, 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Were-Going-Bear-Hunt-First/dp/1406391301', NULL, '£6.99', NULL, NULL, 'Walker Books Ltd — We''re Going on a Bear Hunt: My First 123', 'Similar to the opposites book, focuses on early counting and number recognition in an interactive format.', 'Similar to the opposites book, focuses on early counting and number recognition in an interactive format.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_play_kitchen_household_props', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for budding chefs', 'Little Dutch Wooden Play Kitchen - Mint', 'Little Dutch', 'Scandiborn', 'https://www.scandiborn.co.uk/products/little-dutch-wooden-play-kitchen-mint', NULL, '£129.95', 'in_stock', '3+', 'A beautifully designed wooden play kitchen with an oven, stove, sink, and microwave, encouraging imaginative cooking and role-play.', 'This kitchen is a fantastic choice for nearly two-and-a-half-year-olds, supporting their growing interest in pretend play and mimicking adult activities. Its sturdy wooden construction ensures durability for years of play. It''s a ''buy'' if you have the space and budget, offering excellent value for sustained engagement. The stage shift from simple copying to running tiny scenes is well supported here.', 'The Little Dutch kitchen is highly rated for its quality and aesthetic, fitting perfectly with the ''I''m making pretend worlds'' cluster. Its realistic features encourage detailed role-play, which is crucial for this age band''s cognitive development. The durable wooden design ensures it will withstand enthusiastic play.', 'While listed as 3+, many reviews indicate it''s suitable for younger toddlers, especially with supervision. It''s a larger item, so consider space availability.', 'buy', true, 'A strong gift if there is space and the family does not already have one.', 'If space is tight, a small tea set or pan-and-spoon basket can do the same job.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://learningbugs.co.uk/blogs/play-and-learning/little-dutch-kitchen-is-it-worth-it-uk-review-2026', 'https://www.scandiborn.co.uk/products/little-dutch-wooden-play-kitchen-mint', 'https://thekidcollective.co.uk/products/little-dutch-wooden-play-kitchen-mint-1']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_play_kitchen_household_props', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for compact spaces', 'Chad Valley Wooden Table Top Mini Kitchen Roleplay', 'Chad Valley', 'Argos', 'https://www.argos.co.uk/product/7658747', NULL, '£18.00', 'in_stock', '3+', 'A compact wooden tabletop kitchen with mini stove and sink, perfect for small spaces and encouraging early role-play.', 'This mini kitchen is an excellent ''borrow'' or ''buy_pre_loved'' option for families with limited space, or as an introduction to pretend play. It allows for the same imaginative scenarios as larger kitchens but in a more manageable size. It supports the stage shift by providing simple props for language and memory development.', 'Its small footprint makes it accessible for many homes, and its wooden construction offers durability. It''s a great entry-level option for pretend play, aligning with the cluster''s focus on simple props for imaginative worlds.', 'Accessories are minimal, so additional play food or utensils might be desired. Best suited for floor play or a low table.', 'buy_pre_loved', true, 'A good gift for families with limited space or as an add-on to existing play sets.', 'Excellent for small spaces; can be easily stored away when not in use.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.argos.co.uk/product/7658747']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_play_kitchen_household_props', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for classic role-play', 'KidKraft Vintage Play Kitchen - White', 'KidKraft', 'KidKraft (direct)', 'https://www.kidkraft.com/products/vintage-play-kitchen-white', NULL, '£259.99', 'in_stock', '3+', 'A classic wooden play kitchen with realistic features like an ice maker, phone, and ample storage, designed for immersive role-play.', 'The KidKraft Vintage Play Kitchen is a timeless ''buy'' for families seeking a durable and engaging role-play experience. Its detailed design and interactive elements encourage children to develop complex pretend scenarios, moving beyond simple actions to full ''scenes''. This aligns well with the stage shift towards more elaborate imaginative play.', 'This kitchen is consistently praised for its robust construction and engaging features, making it a staple for pretend play. It provides a rich environment for children to explore ''helper jobs'' and ''little figures'' within their pretend worlds.', 'Assembly can be time-consuming. While recommended for 3+, many parents introduce it earlier with supervision. It''s a significant investment, so consider long-term play value.', 'buy', true, 'A strong gift that offers lasting play value and can be passed down.', 'A larger item that requires dedicated play space, but its durability makes it a worthwhile investment.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.kidkraft.com/products/vintage-play-kitchen-white', 'https://www.parents.com/best-play-kitchens-8421405']::text[], 'none'),
